{"tid":339772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"等巴士個陣後面有個阿叔講野好好笑","createTime":"2017-07-29T10:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T12:42:14.000Z","uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38b7c7b00d5ddea70f249205a2d32e46d0d3d646","tid":339772,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"個阿叔大概係好似肥佬黎咁嘅樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/184144_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F184144_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=01943c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一路用住呢把聲講電話<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/184200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F184200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3769703b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係一路聽佢講電話一路打大概jot低佢講咩 所以有啲甩漏<br />\n<br />\n阿叔：<br />\n個個乜鳩動漫節搞到塞撚到仆街<br />\n轉車轉撚咗黎旺角先<br />\n<br />\n屌我做咩唔聽電話？<br />\n我屌緊你老婆呀<br />\n係呀屌緊你老婆呀<br />\n龍舟掛鼓<br />\n關公射月<br />\n屌到佢腳軟睇醫生<br />\n奶閪？<br />\n我淨係奶余詩曼<br />\n胡定欣都得<br />\n<br />\n我黎緊去日本12日<br />\n鹿兒島神戶大阪新大阪奈良京都東京箱根<br />\n我背撚哂啦我同你講<br />\n六萬幾蚊<br />\n箱根個溫泉9000蚊一晚呀我同你講<br />\n係港紙唔撚係Yen<br />\n千幾年前由呀德川家康到克林頓仲有依家日本個個首相<br />\n有無聽過有馬溫泉呀屌你<br />\n唔係個個都浸到 我就係個到浸<br />\n因為我個妹個老公識人<br />\n<br />\n我個女買咗書未？<br />\n買哂啦三千幾蚊<br />\n有啲新書有啲舊書<br />\n<br />\n屌日本妹？<br />\n我老婆仔女都係哂到如果我屌到日本妹我就真係屌你啦<br />\n最好要18歲以上23歲以下<br />\n係呀屌你老母<br />\n你個女考成點呀 有無第一<br />\n我個女就考到第一<br />\n早幾日係大陸搵個舊相好同埋佢個Frd<br />\n起雙飛 一個口爆一個中出<br />\n<br />\n去韓國？<br />\n唔啦屌留返下次同老婆去<br />\n今次去日本<br />\n好啦好啦你再打比我啦"},{"pid":"0fb780f4a17f898b3f4ec01a7ceb0e5c826ebaa0","tid":339772,"uid":11824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"Oh"},{"pid":"c89d7e78c5c1d084a146fd06a76bf665f79faa26","tid":339772,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Oh</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ea3a2bb084c425ad16d6914dfa91ae7b74a15ed","tid":339772,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad008498fb701e0ab0ebfc98f71c9e8bcc6827c2","tid":339772,"uid":8165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"有d即刻駁咀既味道"},{"pid":"7421ae02be8d3da9a5afcdf058f438837b97fde0","tid":339772,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d即刻駁咀既味道</blockquote><br />\n我都係照直打返個阿叔講過啲咩<br />\n可能我笑點太低 對唔住咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157be896a263ca38d257124078e17645187acceb","tid":339772,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:15:30.000Z","msg":"低級到無論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大街大巷大大聲句句撚/屌其實好撚肉酸"},{"pid":"3ca411e016dc9f390464f3be6c783c4dc7f88a51","tid":339772,"uid":51051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"聽到哩d簡直係污染耳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3839273303cf6fe5fe06180a8cd58307560501","tid":339772,"uid":30465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"幾好笑😂<br />\n你又會記得晒"}]}